Title: Contact High
Actors: Michael Ostrowski, Raimund Wallisch, Alexis Santiago Hernandez, Victor Varnado
Plot: A comedy of absurd situations and misunderstandings. Hans and Max would like to corner the local hot dog market, whereas Harry would prefer to be pampered by his muscular auto mechanics. But a bag with mysterious contents interrupts everyone's plans, and the group of improbable thieves and gangsters suddenly find themselves in Poland's Drogomysl.
Production: Lotus Film, Boje Buck Produktion GmbH [de], Iris Productions, Filmfonds Wien
